<b>(1857–1910)</b><br />
Vassalage of the <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Portugal" title="Kingdom of Portugal">Kingdom of Portugal</a><br />
<b>(1910–1914)</b><br />
Subject of the <a href="/wiki/First_Portuguese_Republic" title="First Portuguese Republic">First Portuguese Republic</a></td>
