<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Matrilineal_succession">Matrilineal succession</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Kingdom_of_Kongo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Matrilineal succession">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>The central Bantu groups which comprised most of the Kongo kingdom passed on status through matrilineal succession.<sup id="cite_ref-22" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-22">[22]</a></sup></p>
